00:08:56.250 --> 00:08:58.250
Sıyırt.

00:09:01.420 --> 00:09:02.750
Güm.

00:09:04.630 --> 00:09:05.960
Gak.

00:09:08.250 --> 00:09:09.790
Natsu!

00:09:32.460 --> 00:09:34.210
Evet!

